e","m":"existing","cf":"high","pid":"74977","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/74977/95e52c73-917d-4b34-af3a-d72c8b5c1597.png"}],"female_count":1,"male_count":3,"unknown_count":0,"inc_total":0,"inc_elected":0,"inc_defeated":0,"new_elected":1},{"ward":"Cliviger with Worsthorne","seats":1,"turnout_pct":52.63,"results_url":"https://burnley.gov.uk/council-democracy/elections-voting/election-results-2026/","candidates":[{"n":"Gavin Theaker","p":"Reform UK","v":1215,"r":1,"e":true,"g":"male","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"121024","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/121024/7140afdd-994e-4e48-860b-588254e15ab0.png","stmt":"Hello, I’m Gavin Theaker, your Reform UK candidate for Lanehead.\nWith over 15 years’ experience in the charity sector, including 10 years working to reduce reoffending, I know what accountability really means.\n \nLike you, I’ve seen the decline in our area — especially when it comes to road safety, local crime, and community issues that consistently go unresolved. That stops now! Lanehead has a voice and a choice — YOURS.\n\nFor far too long, Labour, the Lib Dems, and now the Independents have taken us all for granted. That stops on Tuesday 4th November by voting for myself and Reform UK.\n\nFor the first time in years you have a real choice, to be heard, tackle the issues we all face, and hold decision-makers to account.\n\nThis isn’t just a borough election — it’s an opportunity for Lanehead to move forward with real representation, true accountability, and a voice for everyone, not just a few."},{"n":"Simon John Bonney","p":"Conservative and Unionist Party","v":514,"r":2,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"110908"},{"n":"Affan Khan Burki","p":"Green Party","v":263,"r":3,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"claude","cf":"high","pid":"123223","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/123223/19ad5e3a-5e6f-4a95-8f95-b00527d7eb98.png"},{"n":"Fran